1
00:00:01,950 --> 00:00:03,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodbye.</font>

2
00:00:03,960 --> 00:00:05,220
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodbye.</font>

3
00:00:05,770 --> 00:00:07,090
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Goodbye.</font>

4
00:00:17,900 --> 00:00:19,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It feels unreal...</i></font>

5
00:00:20,030 --> 00:00:22,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>how little I'm sad about it.</i></font>

6
00:00:31,800 --> 00:00:33,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="14"><font face="Times New Roman"><font color="#b4bb59"><b>Three-Year Journal</b></font></font></font></font></font>

7
00:00:41,780 --> 00:00:42,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"Asa."</i></font>

8
00:00:43,500 --> 00:00:49,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"I'm writing this journal to give to you
 when you turn twenty years old."</i></font>

9
00:00:49,790 --> 00:00:52,870
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>"Your name was chosen
 with a great deal of care."</i></font>

10
00:00:52,870 --> 00:00:58,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It embodies the beauty of all new things
 that come with each day.</i></font>

11
00:01:07,770 --> 00:01:08,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Sis...</i></font>

12
00:01:09,440 --> 00:01:14,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>When and why did you grow to hate me?</i></font>

13
00:01:18,340 --> 00:01:19,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="18">{\an8}<font color="#3f392e">Asa's Personal Belongings</font></font></font></font>

14
00:01:20,270 --> 00:01:24,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Moreover, without my own hatred for you,</i></font>

15
00:01:24,480 --> 00:01:28,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial"><font size="12">{\an8}<font color="#2a251d">Asa's Personal Belongings</font></font></font></font>

16
00:01:24,850 --> 00:01:27,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>would I have ever become a writer?</i></font>

17
00:01:35,900 --> 00:01:42,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}<font face="Georgia"><font size="18"><font color="#3b3132">Journal with Witch</font></font></font></font>

18
00:03:01,110 --> 00:03:06,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="12"><font face="Georgia">{\an3}<font color="#ffffff">Episode 6\h\h\h\h\h\h\h\h<font size="20">Overlap</font></font></font></font></font>

19
00:03:04,030 --> 00:03:06,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}Good morning. Late morning, actually.</font>

20
00:03:07,380 --> 00:03:08,470
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ditching today?</font>

21
00:03:08,470 --> 00:03:09,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

22
00:03:09,700 --> 00:03:11,080
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">School.</font>

23
00:03:11,080 --> 00:03:12,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's summer break! As of today.</font>

24
00:03:20,060 --> 00:03:21,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wanna go somewhere?</font>

25
00:03:21,440 --> 00:03:24,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh, no. I have to work...</font>

26
00:03:24,380 --> 00:03:27,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makio-chan, what days do you have off?</font>

27
00:03:27,680 --> 00:03:30,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Days off? I don't really have any.</font>

28
00:03:30,280 --> 00:03:31,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Dang.</font>

29
00:03:31,570 --> 00:03:35,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Except you're home all the time, 
so it's kinda like you're off every day.</font>

30
00:03:36,300 --> 00:03:40,420
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I sorted what looks like junk
from the important documents.</font>

31
00:03:40,420 --> 00:03:43,280
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay. Where are you going?</font>

32
00:03:43,280 --> 00:03:45,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Band practice.</font>

33
00:03:45,440 --> 00:03:49,760
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This one upperclassman keeps
picking on me for being a beginner.</font>

34
00:03:48,390 --> 00:03:55,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font face="Arial Black">{\an8}<font size="14"><font color="#63554f">Heme Iron</font></font></font></font>

35
00:03:49,760 --> 00:03:51,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that about?</font>

36
00:03:51,160 --> 00:03:52,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"Great, it's the newbie."</font>

37
00:03:52,890 --> 00:03:53,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They say that?</font>

38
00:03:53,930 --> 00:03:55,120
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

39
00:03:55,120 --> 00:03:57,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you've already started learning.</font>

40
00:03:57,460 --> 00:03:59,620
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, that's good! I'll use that next time.</font>

41
00:03:59,950 --> 00:04:02,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">"I've already started learning!"</font>

42
00:04:03,330 --> 00:04:04,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Anyways, I'm off!</font>

43
00:04:04,900 --> 00:04:05,900
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sure.</font>

44
00:04:09,790 --> 00:04:14,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Right... She'll be home every day
 until September.</font>

45
00:04:15,300 --> 00:04:19,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Quit it. This was your idea.</font>

46
00:04:32,620 --> 00:04:33,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Lunch...</font>

47
00:04:43,050 --> 00:04:44,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm home.</font>

48
00:04:46,800 --> 00:04:48,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What the heck?!</font>

49
00:04:49,060 --> 00:04:50,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Welcome back.</font>

50
00:04:50,130 --> 00:04:51,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Never mind that!</font>

51
00:04:51,400 --> 00:04:53,740
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This room looked normal before I left!</font>

52
00:04:53,740 --> 00:04:54,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

53
00:04:55,660 --> 00:04:57,790
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, yeah...</font>

54
00:04:58,560 --> 00:05:01,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, I'll clean up in half an hour.</font>

55
00:05:01,640 --> 00:05:03,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on, just do it now!</font>

56
00:05:03,230 --> 00:05:04,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh...</font>

57
00:05:04,930 --> 00:05:06,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Now's not a good time.</font>

58
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:08,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, I've been wondering 
for a while now.</font>

59
00:05:08,950 --> 00:05:10,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How does it even get like this?</font>

60
00:05:10,940 --> 00:05:13,360
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you're always
 forgetting what I tell you!</font>

61
00:05:13,360 --> 00:05:16,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why is that? Why can't you 
do something so simple?</font>

62
00:05:18,270 --> 00:05:20,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why can't I do something so simple?</font>

63
00:05:21,900 --> 00:05:24,590
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's okay. Don't be so down on yourself.</font>

64
00:05:24,590 --> 00:05:28,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No worries. 
A lot of novelists are like you.</font>

65
00:05:28,850 --> 00:05:33,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Although it <i>can</i> get you 
into trouble with your taxes.</font>

66
00:05:33,100 --> 00:05:35,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes, that sounds a lot like me.</font>

67
00:05:35,110 --> 00:05:38,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, you mean that was mandatory?</font>

68
00:05:38,620 --> 00:05:42,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm sorry, um... I don't understand 
this system very well...</font>

69
00:05:43,050 --> 00:05:45,230
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makio? Makio!</font>

70
00:05:45,230 --> 00:05:46,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

71
00:05:46,150 --> 00:05:48,920
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Were you even listening to me?</font>

72
00:05:49,370 --> 00:05:53,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Uh... I guess not really.</font>

73
00:05:53,040 --> 00:05:54,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Darn you.</font>

74
00:05:54,490 --> 00:05:55,730
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My bad.</font>

75
00:05:56,240 --> 00:05:58,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makio, did you do your homework?</font>

76
00:05:58,240 --> 00:05:59,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makio-san?</font>

77
00:05:59,250 --> 00:06:00,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makio.</font>

78
00:06:00,240 --> 00:06:00,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Makio!</font>

79
00:06:01,240 --> 00:06:03,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">H-H-Hang on...</font>

80
00:06:04,490 --> 00:06:05,660
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Give me a minute...</font>

81
00:06:07,260 --> 00:06:09,370
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you need to get that upset?</font>

82
00:06:09,370 --> 00:06:12,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm only stating the obvious.</font>

83
00:06:14,150 --> 00:06:17,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What upsets me is up to me!</font>

84
00:06:17,970 --> 00:06:19,890
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You don't get to decide that for me!</font>

85
00:06:24,130 --> 00:06:28,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's "obvious" to you 
doesn't come so readily to me.</font>

86
00:06:32,540 --> 00:06:36,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My mind is constantly busy.</font>

87
00:06:37,270 --> 00:06:39,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I easily lose sight of things.</font>

88
00:06:40,050 --> 00:06:42,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm a terrible liar.</font>

89
00:06:43,340 --> 00:06:45,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And I'm more comfortable alone.</font>

90
00:06:46,230 --> 00:06:48,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">For whatever reason, I was born this way.</font>

91
00:06:49,330 --> 00:06:51,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just like how you were born 
to hate being alone.</font>

92
00:06:53,420 --> 00:06:58,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not something you get to choose
 or shame others for.</font>

93
00:07:01,090 --> 00:07:05,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just like you can't understand 
the suffocation I feel,</font>

94
00:07:05,180 --> 00:07:08,570
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I can't understand your loneliness.</font>

95
00:07:34,940 --> 00:07:35,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes?</font>

96
00:07:36,260 --> 00:07:40,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I'm sorry. 
I have plans with Asa today.</font>

97
00:07:40,970 --> 00:07:42,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is today Saturday?</font>

98
00:07:42,850 --> 00:07:43,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yes.</font>

99
00:07:43,770 --> 00:07:47,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hey, can Emiri come over on Saturday?</font>

100
00:07:47,150 --> 00:07:48,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hmm...</font>

101
00:07:49,210 --> 00:07:51,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's Saturday already?</font>

102
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:53,270
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Come on in.</font>

103
00:07:56,970 --> 00:07:58,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Something smells good.</font>

104
00:07:58,410 --> 00:08:01,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, I was feeling on edge,
so I'm baking a cake.</font>

105
00:08:01,990 --> 00:08:03,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Feeling on edge?</font>

106
00:08:04,590 --> 00:08:06,300
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Wait, where's Asa?</font>

107
00:08:06,300 --> 00:08:08,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She said she's at the convenience store.</font>

108
00:08:08,520 --> 00:08:10,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You didn't notice?</font>

109
00:08:10,560 --> 00:08:14,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">She may have mentioned it, 
but I can't say for certain.</font>

110
00:08:19,050 --> 00:08:22,610
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">This one's your standard tea. 
And here are a couple of flavored ones.</font>

111
00:08:22,610 --> 00:08:26,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I also have black bean tea, green tea,
roasted brown rice tea... That's expired.</font>

112
00:08:26,490 --> 00:08:29,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, and milk. Have whatever you'd like.</font>

113
00:08:29,930 --> 00:08:32,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nothing is also an option.</font>

114
00:08:33,350 --> 00:08:35,330
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You mean I get to choose?</font>

115
00:08:35,640 --> 00:08:36,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

116
00:08:36,940 --> 00:08:40,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's taking that girl so long?</font>

117
00:08:56,480 --> 00:08:58,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That one, huh? You got it.</font>

118
00:09:21,440 --> 00:09:24,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um... Why aren't you married?</font>

119
00:09:24,950 --> 00:09:26,000
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Huh?</font>

120
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:28,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're not, are you?</font>

121
00:09:28,500 --> 00:09:30,530
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">W-Well, no.</font>

122
00:09:31,380 --> 00:09:33,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why do you ask?</font>

123
00:09:33,790 --> 00:09:35,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's just that...</font>

124
00:09:35,130 --> 00:09:39,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">My parents keep telling me 
I'll get married one day, but...</font>

125
00:09:44,610 --> 00:09:47,930
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not saying this 
just because I'm single,</font>

126
00:09:48,390 --> 00:09:52,910
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">but I don't think it's "normal" to be 
married or "weird" to be unmarried.</font>

127
00:09:54,020 --> 00:09:56,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Naturally, same goes 
for not <i>wanting</i> to get married.</font>

128
00:09:57,030 --> 00:09:59,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's not that I don't want to, but...</font>

129
00:10:05,660 --> 00:10:08,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, then what about someone you like?</font>

130
00:10:09,670 --> 00:10:12,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do you have anyone like that?</font>

131
00:10:12,650 --> 00:10:13,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm not sure.</font>

132
00:10:13,880 --> 00:10:15,040
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh?!</font>

133
00:10:15,620 --> 00:10:20,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I mean, I have someone who
I consider a friend...</font>

134
00:10:20,550 --> 00:10:22,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm fine just being friends.</font>

135
00:10:22,430 --> 00:10:26,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If being your boyfriend makes you hate me,</font>

136
00:10:26,710 --> 00:10:28,460
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'd rather go back to being friends.</font>

137
00:10:29,450 --> 00:10:32,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Please, don't push me away...</font>

138
00:10:35,590 --> 00:10:39,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm back! Sorry about that, Emiri!</font>

139
00:10:39,340 --> 00:10:40,860
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Asa!</font>

140
00:10:40,860 --> 00:10:43,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Guess what? Makio-san and I 
were just talking about love.</font>

141
00:10:43,380 --> 00:10:45,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? No way! You mean Kasamachi-kun?</font>

142
00:10:45,170 --> 00:10:46,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What?! Who's Kasamachi-kun?</font>

143
00:10:46,800 --> 00:10:48,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You call him that?</font>

144
00:10:48,030 --> 00:10:51,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's personal, so I'm not telling.</font>

145
00:10:51,940 --> 00:10:54,140
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an8}But you told Emiri!</font>

146
00:10:52,990 --> 00:10:54,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Oh, the cake's done.</font>

147
00:10:55,260 --> 00:10:56,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want cake.</font>

148
00:10:56,560 --> 00:10:58,840
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It needs to cool down first.</font>

149
00:10:58,840 --> 00:11:02,180
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Once it's cool enough to touch, 
you can take it out of the pan.</font>

150
00:11:02,180 --> 00:11:04,430
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It'll taste better once fully cooled.</font>

151
00:11:04,430 --> 00:11:05,390
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay!</font>

152
00:11:05,390 --> 00:11:07,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">But it smells so good.</font>

153
00:11:07,460 --> 00:11:08,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I dunno if I can wait.</font>

154
00:11:09,520 --> 00:11:11,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Me either!</font>

155
00:11:14,090 --> 00:11:15,850
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry I'm late.</font>

156
00:11:15,850 --> 00:11:18,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">He's a little pampered, 
but I promise he's a good guy.</font>

157
00:11:18,810 --> 00:11:21,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What's that for? Cut me some slack.</font>

158
00:11:21,320 --> 00:11:22,520
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Is beer okay?</font>

159
00:11:22,520 --> 00:11:23,240
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yeah.</font>

160
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:25,490
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll order some other stuff for us too.</font>

161
00:11:25,490 --> 00:11:28,110
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Nice to meet you. I'm Kasamachi.</font>

162
00:11:28,420 --> 00:11:29,670
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'm Koudai.</font>

163
00:11:30,080 --> 00:11:31,030
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hi...</font>

164
00:11:31,370 --> 00:11:33,020
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><font size="14"><font face="Arial">{\an1}<font color="#363e49">Kasamachi</font></font></font></font>

165
00:11:31,370 --> 00:11:33,100
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="12"><font color="#2c4d29">Thanks for today. And the food.</font></font></font></font>

166
00:11:31,370 --> 00:11:36,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="12"><font color="#1c1c1c">My pleasure. It was a nice change of pace
\hfrom eating alone. Let's do it again.</font></font></font></font>

167
00:11:31,370 --> 00:11:36,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an3}<font face="Arial"><font size="12"><font color="#2c4d29">Sure, I'll reach out sometime.</font></font></font></font>

168
00:11:31,370 --> 00:11:36,880
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">{\an1}<font face="Arial"><font size="12"><font color="#1c1c1c">Hey. I feel bad with you coming over and bringing food all the time, so how about we go out for some drinks for a change? Now that Asa's settled in and all</font></font></font></font>

169
00:11:37,950 --> 00:11:40,820
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Hang on. Where's this feeling coming from?</font>

170
00:11:44,890 --> 00:11:47,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, a-are you okay?</font>

171
00:11:47,480 --> 00:11:50,130
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>I'm fine. Excuse me for that.</i></font>

172
00:11:50,640 --> 00:11:51,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Can I help you?</font>

173
00:11:51,830 --> 00:11:55,010
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Oh, right. It's nothing urgent,</i></font>

