338
00:18:56,310 --> 00:18:59,640
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Then I'll have to drag you out 
for a walk every now and then.</font>

339
00:18:59,640 --> 00:19:03,770
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Looking back now, I used 
to be in much better shape.</font>

340
00:19:03,770 --> 00:19:04,830
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Told you.</font>

341
00:19:05,140 --> 00:19:09,710
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">When I go on walks alone, 
my mind starts to wander.</font>

342
00:19:10,280 --> 00:19:13,160
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's nice to walk with someone 
and talk for a change.</font>

343
00:19:13,590 --> 00:19:15,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Just for a change, huh?</font>

344
00:19:15,070 --> 00:19:17,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Yup. You know me too well.</font>

345
00:19:17,990 --> 00:19:20,580
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, it took me long enough to get here.</font>

346
00:19:21,570 --> 00:19:24,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I should've gotten some coffee to go.</font>

347
00:19:25,060 --> 00:19:27,560
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Too bad there isn't 
a coffee shop around here.</font>

348
00:20:00,130 --> 00:20:02,170
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">S-Sorry. Did you not want to?</font>

349
00:20:02,170 --> 00:20:04,340
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">N-No, it's not that.</font>

350
00:20:04,340 --> 00:20:07,990
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Actually, I'm dying to.</font>

351
00:20:07,990 --> 00:20:10,630
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">What? R-R-Really?</font>

352
00:20:11,230 --> 00:20:13,070
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Um, thanks, I think?</font>

353
00:20:13,490 --> 00:20:16,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ugh! I'm just so confused!</font>

354
00:20:16,410 --> 00:20:18,150
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Okay, what's wrong?</font>

355
00:20:18,420 --> 00:20:19,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Confused about what?</font>

356
00:20:20,210 --> 00:20:22,810
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You're important to me.</font>

357
00:20:22,810 --> 00:20:24,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And you're also my friend.</font>

358
00:20:24,500 --> 00:20:27,410
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I feel like I'm sullying that.</font>

359
00:20:27,970 --> 00:20:30,600
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I see you're overthinking things again.</font>

360
00:20:30,600 --> 00:20:34,510
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I'll regret it if I don't 
think things through.</font>

361
00:20:35,910 --> 00:20:37,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Well, you don't need to.</font>

362
00:20:39,370 --> 00:20:43,260
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">We can stay friends. 
I won't meddle in your business.</font>

363
00:20:43,260 --> 00:20:45,550
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">If we desire each other, then fine.</font>

364
00:20:45,550 --> 00:20:47,650
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">And we'll lean on each other
 in times of need.</font>

365
00:20:47,650 --> 00:20:48,440
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">How's that sound?</font>

366
00:20:49,210 --> 00:20:52,050
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Isn't that way too unfair to you?</font>

367
00:20:52,050 --> 00:20:55,690
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">No, it's not. Actually, 
it's more unfair to you.</font>

368
00:20:56,200 --> 00:20:59,320
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I want you to need me around somehow.</font>

369
00:20:59,700 --> 00:21:02,680
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Not that I want you to be down, of course.</font>

370
00:21:04,180 --> 00:21:06,960
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Why can't I do something so simple?</i></font>

371
00:21:07,350 --> 00:21:11,950
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">I don't deserve help from anyone.</font>

372
00:21:11,950 --> 00:21:13,500
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">That's what I keep thinking.</font>

373
00:21:15,450 --> 00:21:18,540
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Why would you say something so sad?</font>

374
00:21:20,740 --> 00:21:22,940
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Sorry, sorry, sorry!</font>

375
00:21:22,940 --> 00:21:25,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Damn, here I go again, 
making the same mistake.</font>

376
00:21:26,500 --> 00:21:28,060
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It's so hard...</font>

377
00:21:28,700 --> 00:21:30,400
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">It really is.</font>

378
00:21:31,280 --> 00:21:34,750
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>Treating someone right...</i></font>

379
00:21:34,750 --> 00:21:36,700
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26"><i>It's such a simple, difficult thing.</i></font>

380
00:21:38,010 --> 00:21:42,970
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">You know, you've always smelled nice.</font>

381
00:21:43,480 --> 00:21:45,480
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Ever since we first met.</font>

382
00:21:51,400 --> 00:21:55,380
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Other men don't smell like this.</font>

383
00:21:58,270 --> 00:21:59,250
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">Do they?</font>

384
00:22:07,200 --> 00:22:08,800
<font face="Roboto Medium" size="26">They don't.</font>

